{"tid":728174,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[公售7月5日] GOT7 香港演唱會 2018 [8月24日-星期五]","createTime":"2018-07-03T15:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T16:29:50.000Z","uid":19208,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3e836fb3aa24235e32211f66e330e0b0b4efd897","tid":728174,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"GOT7 香港演唱會 2018 消息!<br />\n演出日期: 2018年8月24日 (星期五)<br />\n傳聞門票價錢: HK$2380 / $1680 / $1380 / $980 / $580<br />\n演出場館: 亞洲國際博覽館 Arena<br />\n傳聞公開發售: 2018年7月5日10am起 購票通 Cityline<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tickethk.com/images/seating_plans/1396.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tickethk.com%2Fimages%2Fseating_plans%2F1396.jpg&h=f81a5d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGOT7（韓語：갓세븐）是韓國JYP娛樂於2014年推出的7人男子團體。成員有Mark、JB、Jackson、Jr.、Youngjae、BamBam、 Yugyeom，由JB擔任隊長。<br />\n<br />\nGOT7 出身於韓國娛樂界三大巨頭之一 JYP娛樂公司，是JYP 時隔6年再次推出的男子組合，更是JYP 首支HIP HOP 團體。成員來自韓、美、泰、港四地，當中最為港迷熟悉，定必是隊中香港土生土長的前港隊劍擊選手Jackson 王嘉爾，港迷明言已做好準備迎接Jackson 回家!"},{"pid":"633dbe71a38ed3ad4738abfb6cf6cf28e75d5d68","tid":728174,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1095377a1ea71beb5eca4e7adb105c83a67c9f3d","tid":728174,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:09:37.000Z","msg":"有網話改左期<br />\n係唔係真？"},{"pid":"609d1bd10b5b4ad7a0f987ce32a2ec95114b67ea","tid":728174,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1095377a1ea71beb5eca4e7adb105c83a67c9f3d","tid":728174,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:09:37.000Z","msg":"有網話改左期<br />\n係唔係真？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"公售日子***"},{"pid":"8e737de1cf5d740e6633e4364efa68726fb96f42","tid":728174,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609d1bd10b5b4ad7a0f987ce32a2ec95114b67ea"